>> servings: 1

In a mug, mix @flour{1/4%cup}, @sugar{2%tbsp}, @baking powder{1/4%tsp}, @Vanillinzucker{1/4%tsp}, @salt{}

Add some flavor by adding vanilla, spices(cardamom, cinnamon, nutmeg, ...), cocoa, ...

Mix in @milk{3%tbsp} and melted @butter{1%tbsp} too.

Cook in the microwave at low power for ~{75%s}
